Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, docker-compose-plugin | docker-compose
Maintainer: Samuel <lordnns@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Lordnns/MMORPG
Description: MMORPG lab — dedicated gatekeeper VM
 Runs the gatekeeper REST + SSE service on a dedicated VM. Connects to
 a remote Redis.
 .
 Configure /etc/default/mmorpg-gatekeeper (REDIS_URL), then:
   systemctl start mmorpg-gatekeeper
